{"tid":1181830,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜熱刺同普sir","createTime":"2019-06-01T20:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T20:58:40.000Z","uid":11258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6bceec6292e911f878680bf7bd3930e8882fb0f","tid":1181830,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T20:57:28.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】熱刺在周二歐聯4強首回合主場迎戰阿積士力爭球會史上首次殺入決賽，領隊普捷天奴坦言活在夢裡。<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我正活在夢裡</strong></span></span>。其實我已經歷過，5年前帶領熱刺出戰4強就是一個美夢。當你發夢的時候，一定要遠大一點，要無盡甚至超越無盡。」普捷天奴（Mauricio Pochettino）在賽前記者會上說。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加盟熱刺5年來，至今仍然未嚐冠軍滋味</span></span></strong>，普帥表示：「若你問我怎樣把球會帶到另一層次，像皇家馬德里及巴塞隆拿那樣，贏得一個冠軍並不足夠，需要成為歐聯及英超的爭標份子。」<br />\n<br />\n射手哈利卡尼正在養傷，普捷天奴坦言他沒有可能在次回合復出：「他的情況很好，已經可以開始跑步。不過，我們不可以創造任何不能達成的目標，最重要是他進度良好，之後看看情況如何。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以繼續發夢啦賤種熱狗們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\